I PROMISE, PROMISE, PROMISE--

32:46.765 --> 32:51.035
- IS SOMEONE IN THERE?

32:51.070 --> 32:53.710
[retches]

33:01.747 --> 33:03.177
[doorbell buzzes]

33:03.215 --> 33:06.145
- HELLO?

33:08.754 --> 33:11.364
- COME ON UP.

33:11.390 --> 33:14.460
AND GET YOUR COCK OUT.

33:32.344 --> 33:34.484
- HEY, TEDDY.

33:34.513 --> 33:36.523
THANKS AGAIN
FOR THE ELEPHANT UNDERWEAR.

33:36.548 --> 33:37.748
THEY'RE REALLY FUNNY.

33:37.783 --> 33:39.153
- YEAH, RIGHT.

33:39.185 --> 33:42.045
- NO, REALLY.

33:42.088 --> 33:45.088
- I BET YOU WEREN'T EXPECTING
TO SEE DAVID HERE, HUH?

33:45.124 --> 33:47.734
- YEAH,
TALK ABOUT SURPRISES.

33:47.759 --> 33:52.759
- SO, UH, DO YOU THINK YOU TWO
MIGHT, UH, YOU KNOW?

33:52.798 --> 33:57.568
- I DON'T--
I DON'T THINK SO.

33:57.603 --> 34:00.543
- THAT'S TOO BAD.

34:00.572 --> 34:02.342
- SAY, LISTEN,

34:02.374 --> 34:05.214
I KNOW
THERE'S THIS PART OF US

34:05.244 --> 34:08.754
THAT THINKS WE DON'T
DESERVE TO BE LOVED.

34:08.780 --> 34:09.850
- WHAT ARE YOU
TALKING ABOUT?

34:09.880 --> 34:12.150
- L-LET ME FINISH.

34:12.184 --> 34:15.724
SO WE FALL IN LOVE
WITH SOMEONE

34:15.754 --> 34:18.164
WE KNOW WE CAN'T HAVE

34:18.190 --> 34:22.159
AND WHO'S NEVER GOING
TO LOVE US.

34:22.194 --> 34:26.474
AND WE FANTASIZE...

34:28.199 --> 34:29.000
ABOUT THE DAY

34:29.034 --> 34:32.504
WHEN, ALL OF A SUDDEN,
HE REALIZES,

34:32.538 --> 34:35.638
AND SEES EVERYTHING
HE'S BEEN MISSING,

34:35.674 --> 34:38.514
YOU KNOW, AND--AND
ALL OUR DREAMS COME TRUE,

34:38.543 --> 34:41.853
ONLY, UH, YOU KNOW,
THAT DAY NEVER COMES

34:41.880 --> 34:43.480
AND BEFORE YOU KNOW IT,

34:43.514 --> 34:46.614
IT'S YOUR 40th BIRTHDAY,
IT'S YOUR 50th BIRTHDAY,

34:46.652 --> 34:51.292
AND--AND YOU'RE STILL ALONE.

34:54.860 --> 34:59.900
DON'T LET THAT HAPPEN
TO YOU, MICHAEL.

34:59.931 --> 35:03.501
LOVE SOMEONE FOR REAL.

35:06.172 --> 35:09.112
SOMEONE WHO LOVES YOU.

35:16.648 --> 35:21.488
- OH, MY GOD.

35:21.520 --> 35:23.460
TRACY, WHAT ARE YOU
DOING HERE?

35:23.489 --> 35:26.359
- HAPPY BIRTHDAY, MIKE.

35:26.392 --> 35:28.662
- THANKS.
UH, IT'S REALLY WILD.

35:28.694 --> 35:30.634
I--
THEY'RE ALL A LITTLE DRUNK.

35:30.662 --> 35:33.472
I DON'T REAL--
I ONLY KNOW SIX OF THEM.

35:33.499 --> 35:34.769
- YOUR FRIEND BRIAN CALLED.

35:34.800 --> 35:37.870
HE ASKED ME TO COME.
- WHAT?

35:37.903 --> 35:40.243
LOOK, UH,
ARE YOU HUNGRY?

35:40.272 --> 35:41.812
'CAUSE THERE'S THIS, UM,
BURGER PLACE RIGHT NEAR HERE

35:41.840 --> 35:44.240
WE COULD GO GET A BITE--
- TRACY.

35:44.276 --> 35:46.646
I AM SO HAPPY
THAT YOU COULD MAKE IT

35:46.678 --> 35:51.378
TO MICHAEL'S
SURPRISE PARTY.

35:51.417 --> 35:54.787
LET ME INTRODUCE YOU
TO A FEW OF OUR GUESTS.

35:54.820 --> 35:56.320
- BRIAN!

35:56.355 --> 35:59.225
- DAVID.

35:59.258 --> 36:00.458
DAVID, THIS IS TRACY.

36:00.492 --> 36:01.562
TRACY, THIS IS DAVID.

36:01.593 --> 36:02.893
- TRACY, YEAH, WE MET.

36:02.928 --> 36:04.828
- RIGHT, YOU'RE MIKE'S
CHIROPRACTOR.

36:04.863 --> 36:06.373
- RIGHT.

36:06.398 --> 36:11.238
- HE'S ALSO HIS BOYFRIEND.

36:11.270 --> 36:15.540
OH, EXCUSE ME.
EX-BOYFRIEND.

36:15.574 --> 36:16.844
THE FIRST TIME
THEY FUCKED,

36:16.875 --> 36:21.505
