LIKE, THREE TIMES.

36:21.547 --> 36:23.577
[all gasping]

36:29.321 --> 36:31.961
- MIKE.

36:31.990 --> 36:33.960
WHY DON'T YOU BUY
YOUR FRIEND, TRACY, A DRINK?

36:33.992 --> 36:36.962
