YOU HAVEN'T EVEN HAD YOUR CAKE.

36:45.304 --> 36:47.514
- FUCK OFF!

36:49.341 --> 36:51.781
- [spits]
[balloon pops]

36:53.279 --> 36:55.849
- TRACY.

36:58.784 --> 37:02.494
