37:17.969 --> 37:19.339
THE BOYS,
DO YOU LAUGH AT ME?

37:19.371 --> 37:21.471
- NO. NO.

37:21.507 --> 37:24.877
- I MUST BE A BIG JOKE
TO YOU, HUH?

37:24.910 --> 37:27.580
