THE ONE WHO HAS THE CRUSH.

37:27.613 --> 37:29.883
SHE'S SO FUNNY
BECAUSE SHE'S SO STUPID.

37:29.915 --> 37:32.445
- IT'S NOT LIKE THAT,
I SWEAR.

37:32.484 --> 37:35.924
- YOU'RE A LIAR, MIKE.
A LIAR.

37:50.636 --> 37:53.566
- [sniffs]

37:56.542 --> 37:57.642
- HEY.

37:57.676 --> 38:01.746
