FOR THIS SPECIAL OCCASION.

38:01.780 --> 38:04.050
- I'D LIKE TO GET OUT OF HERE,
HOW ABOUT YOU?

38:04.082 --> 38:06.052
- YEAH.

38:06.084 --> 38:09.564
- DON'T FORGET THIS.

38:09.588 --> 38:12.388
- I DON'T WANT IT.

38:12.424 --> 38:15.834
THANKS FOR THE PARTY.

38:18.430 --> 38:19.400
- WELL, BRIAN,

38:19.431 --> 38:22.531
YOU REALLY KNOW
HOW TO THROW A BIRTHDAY BASH.

38:22.568 --> 38:27.538
- TOO BAD ALL GOOD THINGS
MUST COME TO AN END.

38:27.573 --> 38:29.413
- WELL, WELL, WELL.

38:29.441 --> 38:30.781
IS ANYONE SURPRISED?

38:30.809 --> 38:32.509
THAT'S THE WAY
HE TREATS PEOPLE.

38:32.544 --> 38:34.384
AM I RIGHT?

38:34.413 --> 38:36.083
I MEAN,
IS THERE ANYONE HERE TONIGHT

38:36.114 --> 38:39.994
THAT HASN'T BEEN FUCKED
BY BRIAN KINNEY

38:40.018 --> 38:42.818
ONE WAY OR ANOTHER?

38:42.854 --> 38:45.424
- WELL, WHAT DO YOU KNOW?

38:45.457 --> 38:49.427
NOW MICHAEL HAS BEEN, TOO.

38:49.461 --> 38:53.701
- SO YOU FINALLY GAVE HIM
WHAT HE WANTED.

38:53.732 --> 38:56.542
GOOD FOR YOU.

39:00.606 --> 39:02.906
- HOW COULD YOU HAVE
DONE THAT TO HIM, BRIAN?

39:02.941 --> 39:07.481
YOUR BEST FRIEND
IN THE WHOLE WORLD.

39:15.687 --> 39:18.657
- WELL?

39:18.690 --> 39:20.630
AREN'T YOU GOING
TO MAKE YOUR BIG EXIT, TOO?

39:20.659 --> 39:23.999
- NO.

39:24.029 --> 39:24.799
YOU'RE GOING
TO NEED SOMEONE

39:24.830 --> 39:27.830
TO HELP YOU
CLEAN UP THIS MESS.

39:38.143 --> 39:40.583
- UH, COME IN,
TAKE OFF YOUR THINGS--

39:40.612 --> 39:45.152
YOUR COAT--
AND RELAX.

39:45.183 --> 39:46.893
- THANKS.

39:46.918 --> 39:49.018
- WOULD YOU LIKE A DRINK?

39:49.054 --> 39:53.094
- NO, I THINK
I'VE HAD ENOUGH.

39:53.124 --> 39:54.694
THAT WAS SOME PARTY, HUH?

39:54.726 --> 39:56.756
- IT HAD ITS MOMENTS.

39:56.795 --> 40:00.165
- LIKE WHEN YOU
PUNCHED HIM.

40:00.198 --> 40:02.628
- HE DESERVED IT.

40:02.668 --> 40:04.538
- HE DESERVED WORSE.

40:04.570 --> 40:09.710
- I-I JUST DON'T WANT
TO TALK ABOUT IT RIGHT NOW.

40:11.510 --> 40:13.040
- I MISSED YOU.

40:13.078 --> 40:14.648
- HAVE YOU?

40:14.680 --> 40:16.780
- YEAH, I HAVE.

40:29.895 --> 40:34.695
- I-I'M NOT SURE
WHAT'S HAPPENING HERE RIGHT NOW.

40:37.703 --> 40:39.813
- I WANT TO TAKE YOU UP
ON YOUR OFFER,

40:39.838 --> 40:42.168
TO LIVE TOGETHER.

40:42.207 --> 40:46.907
I WANT
TO GIVE IT A SHOT.

40:46.945 --> 40:50.975
- I'M NOT
A CONSOLATION PRIZE.

40:53.051 --> 40:57.521
- I KNOW THAT.

40:57.556 --> 40:59.926
YOU'RE FIRST PRIZE.

40:59.958 --> 41:01.928
- YOU'RE SURE?

41:01.960 --> 41:06.670
- I'M 30.

41:06.698 --> 41:11.068
IT'S TIME I SETTLED DOWN
AND TOOK ON SOME RESPONSIBILITY.

41:11.102 --> 41:12.542
- OH, UH-UH.

41:12.571 --> 41:16.741
NOW YOU'RE MAKING ME
SOUND LIKE LIFE INSURANCE.

41:16.775 --> 41:20.075
- WELL, IN A WAY,
YOU ARE.

41:23.014 --> 41:27.594
DO YOU STILL LOVE ME?

41:27.619 --> 41:32.219
BECAUSE I LOVE YOU.

41:36.261 --> 41:38.161
- COME.

42:00.051 --> 42:04.061
- HE ASKED ME TO PICK UP
THE STUFF HE LEFT.

42:12.764 --> 42:14.734
HEY, SUNSHINE.

42:14.766 --> 42:16.196
YOU GOT SOME TABLES
TO BUS.

42:16.234 --> 42:19.144
- [groans]

42:19.170 --> 42:21.270
I DON'T FEEL SICK.

42:21.306 --> 42:23.266
MARGARITAS ARE DEFINITELY
MY DRINK.

42:23.308 --> 42:26.678
- GET UP.

42:41.627 --> 42:43.187
YOU WANT SOME COFFEE?

42:43.228 --> 42:46.158
- NO, THANKS.

42:49.234 --> 42:52.674
CHRIST, I WAS PISSED AT YOU
LAST NIGHT.

42:52.704 --> 42:56.984
EVERYBODY WAS.
IS.

42:57.008 --> 42:59.948
