OF MY CUSSING YOU OUT,

42:59.978 --> 43:04.818
I FINALLY
FIGURED IT OUT.

43:04.850 --> 43:08.790
YOU CAN'T DO ANYTHING QUIETLY,
CAN YOU?

43:08.820 --> 43:13.260
