OFF A FUCKING CLIFF.

43:22.033 --> 43:23.373
- YEAH, I HAD TO.

43:23.401 --> 43:28.341
OTHERWISE, HE WOULD HAVE
JUST FOLLOWED ME AROUND FOREVER.

43:30.308 --> 43:33.808
- YEAH, I GUESS
HE WOULD HAVE.

43:36.982 --> 43:38.382
JUSTIN!

43:38.416 --> 43:42.016
- I'M BRUSHING MY TEETH.

43:42.053 --> 43:43.793
- YOU LOANED HIM
YOUR TOOTHBRUSH?

43:43.822 --> 43:45.262
- I HAVE A SUPPLY.

43:45.290 --> 43:48.430
- OH.

43:48.459 --> 43:50.929
- IT WAS THE ONLY WAY.

43:50.962 --> 43:54.972
- THIS DAVID,
HE'S GOOD FOR HIM.

43:55.000 --> 43:58.140
- YEAH, THAT WON'T LAST.

43:58.169 --> 44:01.039
- MAYBE NOT.

44:01.072 --> 44:03.882
BUT HE SHOULD AT LEAST
GIVE IT A TRY.

44:03.909 --> 44:06.339
- SO, HOW'S HE DOING?

44:06.377 --> 44:10.777
- TRYING TO FIGURE OUT WHY HIS
BEST FRIEND WOULD BETRAY HIM.

44:10.816 --> 44:12.276
OF COURSE,
HE DOESN'T REALIZE

44:12.317 --> 44:16.147
THAT IT'S THE BEST THING
THAT COULD EVER HAPPEN,

44:16.187 --> 44:19.057
THAT YOU DID HIM A FAVOR.

44:19.090 --> 44:24.060
THAT MAYBE NOW HE CAN FINALLY
HAVE A CHANCE TO HAVE A LIFE.

44:25.096 --> 44:28.066
- OKAY.
I'M READY TO GO.

44:45.050 --> 44:48.150
- YOU TAKE CARE,
KIDDO.

44:51.823 --> 44:54.693
THANK YOU.

45:26.391 --> 45:28.991
- WELL, HELLO,
EARLY BIRDS.

45:29.027 --> 45:31.297
- HI.
CAN WE SKIP THE CHIT-CHAT?

45:31.329 --> 45:32.299
WE'VE BEEN HERE
FOR AN HOUR.

45:32.330 --> 45:34.800
- HOUR AND A HALF.

45:34.833 --> 45:37.103
- JUST, UH, JUST GIVE IT
TO ME STRAIGHT.

45:37.135 --> 45:39.165
- OH, THE--THE MESSAGE
I LEFT FOR YOU ON FRIDAY.

45:39.204 --> 45:40.244
- YEAH.

45:40.271 --> 45:42.511
- WELL, UM,
HERE'S THE SITUATION.

45:42.540 --> 45:44.310
- OKAY,
SPARE ME THE, YOU KNOW,

45:44.342 --> 45:46.442
THE "WARM HIM UP,
LET HIM DOWN EASY" SPEECH.

45:46.477 --> 45:48.847
