45:48.880 --> 45:51.150
- YOUR CHECK BOUNCED.

45:51.182 --> 45:52.322
- WHAT?

45:52.350 --> 45:53.520
- YOUR CHECK BOUNCED.

45:53.551 --> 45:56.021
INSUFFICIENT FUNDS.

45:56.054 --> 45:57.994
- PERFECT.
HOW MUCH?

45:58.023 --> 46:00.263
- $60.

46:00.291 --> 46:02.091
- HERE.
YOU'RE PAYING ME BACK.

46:02.127 --> 46:03.797
- OKAY, WHO GIVES A SHIT
ABOUT 60 BUCKS?

46:03.829 --> 46:04.659
I'LL LEAVE IT TO YOU
IN MY WILL.

46:04.695 --> 46:07.865
UM, CAN I HAVE
MY TEST RESULTS, PLEASE?

46:07.899 --> 46:10.369
- YOU'RE FINE.

46:10.401 --> 46:13.271
CONGRATULATIONS.

46:16.074 --> 46:17.414
- OH, MY GOD.

46:17.442 --> 46:20.182
- I TOLD YOU.

46:20.211 --> 46:24.951
- SO, UH, HOW'D YOU LIKE
TO CELEBRATE?

46:29.020 --> 46:31.390
- UH, YOU KNOW WHAT?
I'M SORRY, I CAN'T.

46:31.422 --> 46:34.862
I'M, UH, I'M BUSY.

46:34.893 --> 46:36.963
- OKAY.

46:36.995 --> 46:40.265
WELL, UH, I'LL SEE YOU
AROUND, GUYS.

46:40.298 --> 46:44.368
HAVE A NICE DAY.

46:47.605 --> 46:49.605
- HE'S CUTE.

46:49.640 --> 46:53.280
IF YOU DON'T WANT HIM,
I'LL TAKE HIM.

46:53.311 --> 46:55.311
- YOU CAN HAVE HIM.

46:55.346 --> 46:58.046
I MADE A PROMISE TO GOD.

46:58.083 --> 47:00.453
- A PROMISE TO GOD?
WHAT PROMISE TO GOD?

47:00.485 --> 47:04.055
- I PRAYED AND, UH,
AND TOLD GOD

47:04.089 --> 47:06.189
THAT IF I WERE NEGATIVE,

47:06.224 --> 47:09.034
I WOULD NEVER HAVE SEX
WITH ANOTHER MAN.

47:09.060 --> 47:11.460
AND I'M NEGATIVE.

47:11.496 --> 47:17.096
SO I CAN NEVER
TOUCH A MAN AGAIN.

47:20.571 --> 47:22.211
- UH-HUH.

